            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the pizza is cooking, heat a pot with a drizzle of<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium heat for 1-2 min or until very hot</p><p>Add your <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to a small heatproof bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Carefully pour the heated oil into the bowl, give it a good mix up and set aside for later – this is your <strong>chilli oil</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
